query:
SELECT
            light_cones.id,
            light_cones.rarity,
            light_cones_text.name,
            COUNT(*)
        FROM
            warps
        LEFT JOIN
            light_cones
        ON
            light_cones.id = light_cone
        LEFT JOIN
            light_cones_text
        ON
            light_cones_text.id = character AND light_cones_text.language = $2
        WHERE
            uid = $1
        AND
            light_cone IS NOT NULL
        GROUP BY
            light_cones.id,
            light_cones.rarity,
            light_cones_text.name
        ORDER BY 
            rarity, id
